Job Description
Primary Skill: Java ArchitectMandatory Skill:Minimum 2 Yrs work experience as Java ArchitectMinimum 10 Yrs experience in Java / J2EE technologies.Hands of technology development in Java/J2EE areas like Restful Web services, database transactions, development of highly scalable and available web applications, exposure to HTML5, advanced Java Script.Ownership of architecture, review of technical progress of Agile teams, be point of contact with sales / senior management.Should be good at Java programming and hands on experience in software development practices like unit testing, code reviews, automatic deployment tools.Agile methodologies, and people management and good communication skill.
